title: Australian diary. No. 005

brief_description: This cinemagazine features the following items: swimming instruction classes in New South Wales; problems with traffic in Melbourne; First Nations people show their skill with the stockwhip; Sulman architectural awards and strange animals at the Melbourne Zoo.
